result.adr_address: 8 Landale St, Wan Chai, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 8 Landale St, Wan Chai, Hong Kong
result.name: Dalat Vietnamese Restaurant

reviews.text:
Service : 65marks
Foods : 25marks
Price : 25marks

Ordered a Vietnamese beef flat noodle in soup, delivered in 2 minutes. However it was cold, the raw beef slices were no way to made hot or cooked. The soup was not pure beef soup, I could taste something else.

No appetite to finish it, this is poor!

I won't go there again!

Had the raw beef pho and spring rolls. Really tasty. I would say the broth has the best flavour of any pho outside of Vietnam.

Prices are very cheap and Dalat is very popular with the local people.

I will certainly return.
Won't be disappointed with grilled chicken, pork chop or pork neck. Either with rice or vermicelli. Good value for money.

Went for lunch early when it was less busy, was OK. Get busy near 12 and start to get packed. I would say the portion is reasonable for its price and food is OK. Good if you want something quick. Oh and lunch meun include a HK style hot drink, and not available in English unfortunately...
Juicy pork neck, very reasonable price

result.adr_address: 香港灣仔蘭杜街8號
result.name: 大叻越南牛肉粉餐廳

reviews.text:
晚上在灣仔工作， 碰巧路過一年前 嘗試過的大叻越南牛肉河粉餐廳。用到越南牛肉河來做招牌那招牌菜定當是生牛肉河了。果然一年後依然可保持水準。湯頭清甜且鮮。牛肉仍然保持鮮嫩。以今時今日牛肉價錢有這樣的份量已值回票價了。
稱讚完就要彈了。 今次使了香茅雞中翼$48六隻，失望的是純粹是炸漿雞翼而上面放了蔥油而已。完全沒有半點香茅的味道。 甚至乎麥當勞的炸雞翼還炸得好吃過他。所以下次再來時不會再要了。
總括來說價錢在灣仔區算是抵吃的。
是金鐘區內平民食堂，上菜速度非常快，適合上班一族
炭燒香茅豬扒飯，有兩大塊豬扒，還有炒高麗菜(椰菜)作為配菜，好吃！👍🏻
價錢以灣仔區來講算平，食物也算好味!
